    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款全新的剧情交互探索游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏突破大胆创新，将会融合多个优秀游戏玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用户化身男主角林风，与三位长相、性格都大相径庭的美女相识，并与她们展开刺激的恋爱之旅，而这在过程当中，一举成为她们心目中的英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们在游戏的基础上计划加入更多玩法，尽可能让一款线性剧情游戏“更自由”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关都有自由操纵环节，玩家在一个小型的箱庭地图中自主寻找线索，每个线索也可由玩家自行整理主线故事的重要要素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras/d3d513c638261fb807b2146113957448.avif?t=1726902043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras_big/d3d513c638261fb807b2146113957448.avif?t=1726902043 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras/340fad95dc7dd8b5b5e0a8d35f7cd81d.avif?t=1726902043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras_big/340fad95dc7dd8b5b5e0a8d35f7cd81d.avif?t=1726902043 width=800 height=466 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras/eb811d801e2ce24a078eed421224babf.avif?t=1726902043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras_big/eb811d801e2ce24a078eed421224babf.avif?t=1726902043 width=800 height=466 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抉择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家游戏中将会面临不同的抉择，不同的抉择决定了不同的剧情走向，甚至可能会影响结局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras/99981fb2ad109b77529edff2fcf3d352.avif?t=1726902043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras_big/99981fb2ad109b77529edff2fcf3d352.avif?t=1726902043 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >梦魇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中特殊的模式<strong><i><u>梦魇模式</u></i></strong>，在这里你们可以去探索主线游戏之外的不同的游戏故事，在林风的噩梦中体验额外的剧情，在此游戏中以RPG游戏元素进行；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras/3f2777afe3ec32700aa15a0345212eae.avif?t=1726902043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028120/extras_big/3f2777afe3ec32700aa15a0345212eae.avif?t=1726902043 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
